â¢ Carolina VERA (University of Buenos Aires, Argentina)<br />
â¢ Alistair WOODWARD (University of Auckland, New Zealand)</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">**International Council for Science (ICSU) President Gordon McBean</p></blockquote>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><strong>Financial disclosure note</strong>: <em>My travel costs were covered by conference sponsors because I was a presenter (<a href="//www.commonfuture-paris2015.org/Blog/Zoom-blog.htm?Zoom=7a7a817cca663f5f29a2114aad33bb17&amp;SType=">on the media and climate</a>; more on that soon). But there were, and remain, no constraints on what I write or say.</em></p>
	</div>
